race.comment: GARDEN OF GRACE (1) is still a maiden after four runs. Was in the market last time out but didn't live up to market expectations, finishing fourth over 1106m at Saratoga (Turf). Rates highly in this field and can turn things around. TAHILA (2) didn't make an impact at her last run before going for a spell on 26/07/2025, finishing sixth and beaten 5 lengths over 1710m at Saratoga (Turf). Looks a winning chance. FIVE DOZEN ROSES (5) is a four-start maiden who has been in the money at her last couple of runs, the latest when third over 1106m at Saratoga (Turf). Sure to be right in this. FIFI LA FUME (3) is yet to break through after 12 starts but not far off a win. Placed two back then missed the frame but was thereabouts last time over 1106m at Saratoga (Turf). Chance on best figures and worth including.
